**

# Dashboard build context
!dashboard/
!dashboard/**

# OHIF is copied by docker/ohif-v3.7/Dockerfile. Without these exceptions,
# `COPY ohif-viewer app` receives an empty build context and fails.
!ohif-viewer/
!ohif-viewer/**

# Runtime/release configuration embedded by the dashboard image.
!config/
!config/release/
!config/release/**
